dataset.title: Grand Island Zoning Map
dataset.description:
This is the zoning designations for the City of Grand Island and it's extra-territorial jurisdiction. There are also five zoning overlay codes which will overlap zoning designations and have additional requirements or specifications that are detailed at Chapter 36 of the Grand Island City Code

The five zoning overlays are:
  • A - Airport Zone
  • B2-AC - Arterial Commercial Overlay Zone
  • Gateway Corridor
  • M - Manufactured Home Overlay Zone
  • MD - Manufactured Home Overlay Zone
